locality: Diancang Shan mt range. Vicinity of Huadianba herbal medcine farm. 25°53'N, 100°01'E; 2900-3300 m
Yunnan Province, China. Dali Xian, E side of Diancang Shan mountain range, Vicinity of Yinglofeng.

Vicinity of village of Rizui (Tibetan name = Riza); on steep S- to W-facing slopes above village along trail to oak and pine forest (matsutake harvest site); steep rocky S- to W-facing slopes along trail above village, scrub vegetation, low shrubs with scattered Platyclados; scattered low shrubs
Along the W side of the Nu Jiang, at Shangdang, N of Gongshan.
